snippet.title: Shrimp Magicality
snippet.description:
Explore nightmares and sweet dreams. Shrimp Magicality is an adventure game that is focused on exploration. You play as ‘The Professor,’ a narcoleptic academic, wandering around a fictionalized Seattle. Experience her wildest dreams, as she dozes off throughout The Ave.  

Meet quirky characters, discover a colorful world, and try to get some rest.
